{"tid":866612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攝製隊幾經辛苦，終於搵到阿金","createTime":"2018-10-18T04:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T04:32:01.000Z","uid":131064,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"549e3293a1952fd9df3d8dc1391ac8910815cb19","tid":866612,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>喺好耐以前，啲女人認為，身上有塊閪，腳下有塊土地喺唔夠嘅。所&shy;以佢地不惜離鄉別井，漂泊半生，走到遍遠嘅世界角落，去打劫毒撚&shy;。攝製隊幾經辛苦，終於搵到阿金，佢憑住一塊鑲金肥閪，去開拓&shy;佢嘅夢想。有雞嘅地方就有嫖俠，而有嫖俠嘅地方，就必然會有勞資糾紛。&shy;喺賣身嘅過程，我哋固然見盡滄桑。而其實每一隻雞嘅背後，都有一&shy;個「盪氣迴腸」嘅套餐。喺聽晚，我哋再同大家尋找一個「流散失&shy;落」嘅臭閪血淚史。﻿</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f447e082c0e422045d9a59b871ac09fc863c3086","tid":866612,"uid":52221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:10:41.000Z","msg":"有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e2ec2cede091bce3401ecc03b1574ddf7712fc","tid":866612,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:16:44.000Z","msg":"嗰背影音樂即時出咗嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c562686ce46c46be4b34ed83db6a243a34a896","tid":866612,"uid":23552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:18:34.000Z","msg":"好感動"},{"pid":"ddce4f597432b5364c9af6e72b592a944fc17cef","tid":866612,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5706e242981d654e36e9399b4b5f84fcc6534ce6","tid":866612,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:22:52.000Z","msg":"一講完個「史」字就起音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"